  "detailed_description": "<br>Welcome to Magnificent Bay City! Listen to the music in the evening while you enjoy this wonderful auto-generated fireworks show! You can also hit the fireworks box to release various colors of fireworks!<br>Plus, you can edit your custom fireworks show in the exclusive studio afterwards!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/eca80abd0c9beb7a02ffeb7fbe91d2c6.webp?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=20 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current features:</h2><strong>VR support:</strong> Support in situ range exclusive VR fireworks show viewing experience.<br><br><strong>Multiple fireworks:</strong> Automatically generate and display a dazzling variety of fireworks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/2067f2d45e63e961cf52ed67408c676f.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/2067f2d45e63e961cf52ed67408c676f.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/2067f2d45e63e961cf52ed67408c676f.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Musical climax with super fireworks!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/1501e629896adff1718b9bc0b6108c84.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/1501e629896adff1718b9bc0b6108c84.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/1501e629896adff1718b9bc0b6108c84.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Procedurally generated fireworks show: import your own music, and the core program will analyze and display a fireworks show that fits on its own.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/950975d91ba180f86c87da907901a87a.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/950975d91ba180f86c87da907901a87a.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/950975d91ba180f86c87da907901a87a.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Hit the fireworks box:</strong> Hit the colorful fireworks box to release the brilliant fireworks. The harder you hit, the more fireworks you'll release!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/fcc8be1affc30efcfe145a79f142029b.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/fcc8be1affc30efcfe145a79f142029b.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/fcc8be1affc30efcfe145a79f142029b.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Lasers and lights:</strong> Oscillating color-changing lasers, as well as lights and green lasers that flash to the rhythm.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/353b038657ca35a5f96355ecc9d13a68.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/353b038657ca35a5f96355ecc9d13a68.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/353b038657ca35a5f96355ecc9d13a68.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Comes with music:</strong> Comes with 5 different styles of music for enjoyment.<br><br><strong>List Play:</strong> You can add any music to the list, and then it will be displayed in order automatically! Support fireworks show file or generate fireworks show in real time!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/bc7dae22f3676be8396800744cd3d271.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/bc7dae22f3676be8396800744cd3d271.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/bc7dae22f3676be8396800744cd3d271.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Viewing locations:</strong> Feel free to choose the location where you want to see the fireworks show.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/e19cddba9c1a55f7d3d0a8263c05c1c1.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/e19cddba9c1a55f7d3d0a8263c05c1c1.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/e19cddba9c1a55f7d3d0a8263c05c1c1.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/eca80abd0c9beb7a02ffeb7fbe91d2c6.webp?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><strong>Fireworks Show Studio:</strong> Quickly edit your own exclusive fireworks show performance!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/b74ce9b1514e00923984867de31aad0c.poster.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/b74ce9b1514e00923984867de31aad0c.webm?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/b74ce9b1514e00923984867de31aad0c.mp4?t=1719624949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Select an existing show music file, play it to the location you want to change, and place and remove fireworks cards in the sandbox!<br>All fireworks categories including Super Fireworks are supported.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Development Roadmap:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/0f43836a49b67506be5c1f74a3ad9976.avif?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=500 /></span><br>Single music effect enhancement -> Interactive effect enhancement -> Environment enhancement -> Performance optimization -> Multi music -> Multiplayer -> Editor -> Mod support<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1901580/extras/eca80abd0c9beb7a02ffeb7fbe91d2c6.webp?t=1719624949\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br>A bunch of new features are being planned and worked on, so feel free to let me know if you have any questions on the Discord channel, the Steam community, or by sending me an email!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thanks again for choosing to play Music & Fireworks Show!</h2></h2>",
